{"type": "article", "id": 20362, "title": "圆柱形鱼缸", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-07T07:36:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122340yCsGWRYbTnPij6K5.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t瑞典设计师 Charles Törnros 不满意现有鱼缸看起来笨重，电缆搭配很难看，做了这个家庭使用的圆柱形的鱼缸。可以最大面积观察鱼缸的内部，远看像一盏小灯。鱼缸两头有木质的圆柱，作为基础和盖子，也是可以替换的。两头的圆木对比中间的透明，让鱼缸像是漂浮在空中。灯光从下面发出，照射到顶部时再反射到水里。空气过滤器也安装在了下面，使鱼缸不会显得突兀。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122338IDmXE1BKkCM4lq65.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122338pTZBMHji0aVGREcC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.31666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122339WHn0S4GFUpZh6P3g.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.52\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122339KQLDHYJ3c2slWgRq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.58666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}